      "source": [
        "import pandas as pd\n",
        "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
        "import seaborn as sns\n",
        "\n",
        "# Load the dataset\n",
        "df = pd.read_csv('/content/student-por.csv')\n",
        "\n",
        "# Show basic info\n",
        "print(\"Dataset loaded. Shape:\", df.shape)\n",
        "print(\"\\nColumns:\", df.columns.tolist())\n",
        "\n",
        "# Define performance categories based on final grade (G3)\n",
        "def performance_category(grade):\n",
        "    if grade >= 15:\n",
        "        return 'Excellent'\n",
        "    elif grade >= 10:\n",
        "        return 'Good'\n",
        "    elif grade >= 5:\n",
        "        return 'Average'\n",
        "    else:\n",
        "        return 'Poor'\n",
        "\n",
        "# Add performance column\n",
        "df['Performance'] = df['G3'].apply(performance_category)\n",
        "\n",
        "# Show category distribution\n",
        "print(\"\\nPerformance category distribution:\\n\", df['Performance'].value_counts())\n",
        "\n",
        "# Plot performance distribution\n",
        "plt.figure(figsize=(8, 5))\n",
        "sns.countplot(data=df, x='Performance', order=['Excellent', 'Good', 'Average', 'Poor'], palette='Set2')\n",
        "plt.title('Student Performance Categories Based on Final Grade (G3)')\n",
        "plt.xlabel('Performance')\n",
        "plt.ylabel('Number of Students')\n",
        "plt.grid(True, axis='y', linestyle='--', alpha=0.7)\n",
        "plt.tight_layout()\n",
        "plt.show()\n",
        "\n",
        "# Select relevant numeric columns for correlation analysis\n",
        "correlation_columns = ['G1', 'G2', 'G3', 'studytime', 'failures', 'absences']\n",
        "correlation_data = df[correlation_columns]\n",
        "\n",
        "# Compute correlation matrix\n",
        "correlation_matrix = correlation_data.corr()\n",
        "\n",
        "# Plot correlation heatmap\n",
        "plt.figure(figsize=(8, 6))\n",
        "sns.heatmap(correlation_matrix, annot=True, cmap='coolwarm', linewidths=0.5)\n",
        "plt.title('Correlation Heatmap: Grades vs Studytime, Failures, Absences')\n",
        "plt.tight_layout()\n",
        "plt.show()"
      ]
    }
